snippet.title: Mon Amour Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch/Steam, 2021)
snippet.description:
Welcome to our one-button, insta-death kissing-action for Nintendo Switch & Steam!

Pre-order Mon Amour for Nintendo Switch here:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/mon-amour-switch/

Wishlist Mon Amour on Steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/982350/_/

Click here to find out more about Mon Amour: https://oh-monamour.com/en/

Click here to find out more about Onion Games: http://oniongames.jp/
 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
